price: Yookiin deddeebi’uu isaanii keessatti (Rabbiin) isaan qabuu (hin sodaatanuu)? Isaan dadhabsiisoo hin taane.
arabic: أَوۡ يَأۡخُذَهُمۡ فِي تَقَلُّبِهِمۡ فَمَا هُم بِمُعۡجِزِينَ

version.title: Oromo translation
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Oromo by Ghaly Ababour Abaghuna, printed in 2009.

meta.transliteration: aw yakhudhahum fī taqallubihim famā hum bimuʿ'jizīna
